title: Various Artists - Best 100 Of 2013 (Indie69)
description:
The best of 2013 has arrived. Please note that this is the best of 
the PLAYLISTS I released this year, and may include one or two older
tracks. Hope you like it.

Its a little daring, different than previous years and VERY carefully
curated. I actually think it turned out better than my 2009 list. But
your mileage may vary.

December (shortened) Playlist coming soon.

After that... see you in 2014!!

Happy holidays and happy new year.
